@startuml UC2_HighLevel_Preventive_Request
title UC2 — Log Preventive Maintenance Request (High-Level)

skinparam Style strictuml
autonumber

actor Technician
participant "Maintenance Management System" as MMS
participant "Notification Service" as Notif
actor Supervisor

Technician -> Technician : Identify scheduled maintenance need
Technician -> MMS : Log preventive maintenance request
MMS -> MMS : Validate and store preventive request
MMS -> Notif : Send new preventive request notification
Notif -> Supervisor : Notify preventive maintenance request
MMS --> Technician : Confirm preventive request logged

@enduml